ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX ashrae: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX ex: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223/data/lbnl-example-2#>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?zone ?propLabel ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint WHERE {\\n  # Zone instances\\n  ?zone a ashrae:Zone .\\n\\n  # Either the Zone has a Property directly …\\n  { ?zone ashrae:hasProperty ?prop }\\n  UNION\\n  # …or the Zone reaches a RoomDomainSpace in two \\""connected\\"" steps and that space contains a Property\\n  { \\n    ?zone ashrae:connected ?intermediate1 .\\n    ?intermediate1 ashrae:connected ?roomSpace .\\n    ?roomSpace a ex:RoomDomainSpace .\\n    ?roomSpace ashrae:contains ?prop .\\n  }\\n\\n  # Property label\\n  ?prop rdfs:label ?propLabel .\\n\\n  # External reference linked to the Property\\n  ?prop ashrae:hasExternalReference ?extRef .\\n\\n  # Only consider external references that are *not* writable\\n  ?extRef brick:writable false .\\n\\n  # Retrieve the two endpoint values\\n  OPTIONAL { ?extRef brick:endpoint ?alcEndpoint }\\n  OPTIONAL { ?extRef brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcEndpoint }\\n}\\nORDER BY ?zone ?propLabel""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 2, 12, 29, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[ToolCallPart(tool_name='sparql_query', args='{""query"": ""SELECT ?hp ?propLabel ?quantity ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint WHERE {\\n  ?hp a <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#WatertoWaterHeatPump> .\\n  ?hp <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#hasProperty> ?prop .\\n  ?prop <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> ?propLabel .\\n  # Find quantities related to this property (QuantifiableObservableProperty?)\\n  ?quantity a <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#QuantifiableObservableProperty> .\\n  ?quantity <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#hasAspect> ?prop .\\n  # Non-writable quantities\\n  ?quantity <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/writable> false .\\n  # ALC endpoint reference via external reference\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?quantity <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#hasExternalReference> ?alcRef .\\n    ?alcRef <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/endpoint> ?alcEndpoint .\\n    FILTER regex(str(?alcEndpoint), \\""ALC\\"", \\""i\\"")\\n  }\\n  # MPC endpoint reference via external reference\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?quantity <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#hasExternalReference> ?mpcRef .\\n    ?mpcRef <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/endpoint> ?mpcEndpoint .\\n    FILTER regex(str(?mpcEndpoint), \\""MPC\\"", \\""i\\"")\\n  }\\n}\\nLIMIT 100""}', tool_call_id='chatcmpl-tool-79ad5d28dc46484da82bf6aea373e580', part_kind='tool-call')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 2, 46, 58, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')
